"{\"uid\": \"metro.co.uk-2024-08-04-know-muffin-man-people-going-wild-swimmers-snack-olympics-21359026\", \"noun_phrases\": [{\"sentence\": \"There have been countless standout moments from theParisOlympics so far - fromC\\u00e9line Dion's incredible performanceat the opening ceremony toTeam GBwinning gold medals in rowing and trampoline.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 192, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"countless standout moments\", \"from\": 16, \"to\": 42}, {\"ngram\": \"theParisOlympics\", \"from\": 48, \"to\": 64}, {\"ngram\": \"Dion's incredible performanceat\", \"from\": 85, \"to\": 116}, {\"ngram\": \"the opening ceremony\", \"from\": 117, \"to\": 137}, {\"ngram\": \"GBwinning gold medals\", \"from\": 145, \"to\": 166}, {\"ngram\": \"rowing\", \"from\": 170, \"to\": 176}, {\"ngram\": \"trampoline\", \"from\": 181, \"to\": 191}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But there is also been one majorly unexpected highlight for some sports fans, and it's all thanks to Norwegian distanceswimmerHenrik Christiansen.\", \"from\": 194, \"to\": 340, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 295, \"end\": 304, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Norwegian_language\", \"score\": 0.8253422142642314, \"rank\": 0.21151063112064356, \"text\": \"Norwegian\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Norwegian_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Norwegian_language\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"one majorly unexpected highlight\", \"from\": 217, \"to\": 249}, {\"ngram\": \"some sports fans\", \"from\": 254, \"to\": 270}, {\"ngram\": \"thanks\", \"from\": 285, \"to\": 291}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The 27-year-old might not take home the gold, but he certainly has won the people's hearts thanks to a series of hilarious TikToks about asnackat the Olympic Village.\", \"from\": 342, \"to\": 508, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 492, \"end\": 507, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Village\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.1584795485134e-18, \"text\": \"Olympic Village\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Village\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Village\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the gold\", \"from\": 378, \"to\": 386}, {\"ngram\": \"the people's hearts\", \"from\": 413, \"to\": 432}, {\"ngram\": \"a series\", \"from\": 443, \"to\": 451}, {\"ngram\": \"hilarious TikToks\", \"from\": 455, \"to\": 472}, {\"ngram\": \"asnackat\", \"from\": 479, \"to\": 487}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Village haspreviously hit headlines for its food, as Andy Anson, the British Olympic Association's chief executive, branded the meals 'inadequate'.\", \"from\": 510, \"to\": 661, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 567, \"end\": 577, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Anson\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Andy Anson\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Anson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Anson\"}, {\"begin\": 583, \"end\": 610, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Olympic_Association\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"British Olympic Association\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Olympic_Association\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Olympic_Association\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The Village\", \"from\": 510, \"to\": 521}, {\"ngram\": \"headlines\", \"from\": 540, \"to\": 549}, {\"ngram\": \"its food\", \"from\": 554, \"to\": 562}]}, {\"sentence\": \"However, Henrik claims there is one item that's definitely worth eating, and he's even rated it an 11/10.\", \"from\": 662, \"to\": 767, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Henrik\", \"from\": 671, \"to\": 677}, {\"ngram\": \"one item\", \"from\": 694, \"to\": 702}]}, {\"sentence\": \"No, it's not a croissant or pain au chocolat that the sports star has fallen for - it's a double chocolate muffin, with large chocolate chips and a gooey chocolate filling.\", \"from\": 769, \"to\": 941, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a croissant or pain au chocolat\", \"from\": 782, \"to\": 813}, {\"ngram\": \"the sports star\", \"from\": 819, \"to\": 834}, {\"ngram\": \"a double chocolate muffin\", \"from\": 857, \"to\": 882}, {\"ngram\": \"large chocolate chips\", \"from\": 889, \"to\": 910}, {\"ngram\": \"a gooey chocolate filling\", \"from\": 915, \"to\": 940}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Henrik has gone viral online after sharing videos of himself eating the muffins, which he says are 'insane' and 'the single greatest thing about the Olympic Village.'\", \"from\": 943, \"to\": 1109, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1092, \"end\": 1107, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Village\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.1584795485134e-18, \"text\": \"Olympic Village\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Village\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Village\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Henrik\", \"from\": 943, \"to\": 949}, {\"ngram\": \"videos\", \"from\": 986, \"to\": 992}, {\"ngram\": \"the muffins\", \"from\": 1011, \"to\": 1022}, {\"ngram\": \"the single greatest thing\", \"from\": 1056, \"to\": 1081}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Many of the clips show him looking lovingly at the snack, with chocolate smeared all over his face.\", \"from\": 1111, \"to\": 1210, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the clips\", \"from\": 1119, \"to\": 1128}, {\"ngram\": \"the snack\", \"from\": 1158, \"to\": 1167}, {\"ngram\": \"chocolate\", \"from\": 1174, \"to\": 1183}, {\"ngram\": \"his face\", \"from\": 1201, \"to\": 1209}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In one video, a fellow athlete shares a look at the inside of Henrik's bedside table, and the drawer is just full of muffins.\", \"from\": 1211, \"to\": 1336, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"one video\", \"from\": 1214, \"to\": 1223}, {\"ngram\": \"a fellow athlete\", \"from\": 1225, \"to\": 1241}, {\"ngram\": \"a look\", \"from\": 1249, \"to\": 1255}, {\"ngram\": \"the inside\", \"from\": 1259, \"to\": 1269}, {\"ngram\": \"Henrik's bedside table\", \"from\": 1273, \"to\": 1295}, {\"ngram\": \"the drawer\", \"from\": 1301, \"to\": 1311}, {\"ngram\": \"muffins\", \"from\": 1328, \"to\": 1335}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'Guys, I think I have a problem,' the swimmer jokes in the caption.\", \"from\": 1338, \"to\": 1405, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a problem\", \"from\": 1360, \"to\": 1369}, {\"ngram\": \"the caption\", \"from\": 1393, \"to\": 1404}]}, {\"sentence\": \"As such, he's become known as the official 'Muffin Man' of the Olympics and he does not seem to be particularly upset about the title - in fact, he's embraced it.\", \"from\": 1407, \"to\": 1569, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the official 'Muffin Man\", \"from\": 1437, \"to\": 1461}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 1466, \"to\": 1478}, {\"ngram\": \"the title\", \"from\": 1531, \"to\": 1540}, {\"ngram\": \"fact\", \"from\": 1546, \"to\": 1550}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The single greatest thing about the Olympic Village so far\\ud83e\\udd24#fyp#muffins#olympics#paris2024#olympictiktok#olympicvillage I HEREBY DECLARE MYSELF AS THE OLYMPIC MUFFIN MAN#fyp#olympics#paris2024#olympictiktok#olympicvillage#muffins@Olympics @paris2024 Those watching his videos are desperate to know absolutely everything they can about the muffins, with some asking for a documentary to be made about them.\", \"from\": 1571, \"to\": 1978, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1607, \"end\": 1622, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Village\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.1584795485134e-18, \"text\": \"Olympic Village\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Village\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Village\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The single greatest thing\", \"from\": 1571, \"to\": 1596}, {\"ngram\": \"#fyp#muffins#olympics#paris2024#olympictiktok#olympicvillage\