eferred Source From the latest Walkers flavours to the secret McDonald's menu, Metro Food has it all @t0tally_not_averie wrote: 'Petition to have him in the next Shrek movie as the muffin man.'\", \"from\": 2732, \"to\": 2941, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2779, \"end\": 2786, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Walkers_Limited\", \"score\": 0.9999999995779945, \"rank\": 2.4628040609173323e-10, \"text\": \"Walkers\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Walkers_Limited\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Walkers_Limited\"}, {\"begin\": 2911, \"end\": 2916, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shrek\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.1266725604427606e-30, \"text\": \"Shrek\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q11424\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shrek\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shrek\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 2736, \"to\": 2738}, {\"ngram\": \"a Preferred Source\", \"from\": 2742, \"to\": 2760}, {\"ngram\": \"the secret McDonald's menu\", \"from\": 2797, \"to\": 2823}, {\"ngram\": \"Metro Food\", \"from\": 2825, \"to\": 2835}, {\"ngram\": \"@t0tally_not_averie\", \"from\": 2847, \"to\": 2866}, {\"ngram\": \"the muffin man\", \"from\": 2923, \"to\": 2937}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And @valkyriefox.jpr shared: 'No better love story than a man and his muffins.'\", \"from\": 2943, \"to\": 3022, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"And @valkyriefox.jpr\", \"from\": 2943, \"to\": 2963}, {\"ngram\": \"No better love story\", \"from\": 2973, \"to\": 2993}, {\"ngram\": \"a man\", \"from\": 2999, \"to\": 3004}, {\"ngram\": \"his muffins\", \"from\": 3009, \"to\": 3020}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Others wanted to know how to make the muffins, and said they'd be spending some time trying to recreate them at home.\", \"from\": 3024, \"to\": 3141, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Others\", \"from\": 3024, \"to\": 3030}, {\"ngram\": \"the muffins\", \"from\": 3058, \"to\": 3069}, {\"ngram\": \"some time\", \"from\": 3099, \"to\": 3108}, {\"ngram\": \"home\", \"from\": 3136, \"to\": 3140}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Chefs have even been sharing their own recipes for 'dupes'.\", \"from\": 3142, \"to\": 3201, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Chefs\", \"from\": 3142, \"to\": 3147}, {\"ngram\": \"their own recipes\", \"from\": 3171, \"to\": 3188}, {\"ngram\": \"dupes\", \"from\": 3194, \"to\": 3199}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Guess who is competing today?#OlympicMuffinMan#Paris2024#MuffinMan I GET THE HYPE.\", \"from\": 3203, \"to\": 3286, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"THE HYPE\", \"from\": 3276, \"to\": 3284}]}, {\"sentence\": \"(but only the middle part)#parisolympicschocolatemuffin#parisolympicsgamesvillage#paris2024#parisolympics#parisolympicsdininghall Everyone is talking about the Olympic Chocolate Muffin, especially @Henrik Christiansen who made it go viral on TikTok this week.\", \"from\": 3287, \"to\": 3547, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3531, \"end\": 3537, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/TikTok\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.513997469723354e-54, \"text\": \"TikTok\", \"types\": [\"Q7397\", \"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/TikTok\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/TikTok\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Everyone\", \"from\": 3417, \"to\": 3425}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic Chocolate Muffin\", \"from\": 3443, \"to\": 3471}, {\"ngram\": \"Christiansen\", \"from\": 3492, \"to\": 3504}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Here's my copycat recipe: a warm, decadent double chocolate muffin filled with a rich chocolate ganache!\", \"from\": 3549, \"to\": 3653, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my copycat recipe\", \"from\": 3556, \"to\": 3573}, {\"ngram\": \"a warm, decadent double chocolate muffin\", \"from\": 3575, \"to\": 3615}, {\"ngram\": \"a rich chocolate ganache\", \"from\": 3628, \"to\": 3652}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\ud83c\\udf6b \\ud83d\\udd17 FULL RECIPE LINKED IN MY BIO!\", \"from\": 3654, \"to\": 3687, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"\\ud83c\\udf6b \\ud83d\\udd17 FULL RECIPE LINKED\", \"from\": 3654, \"to\": 3676}, {\"ngram\": \"MY BIO\", \"from\": 3680, \"to\": 3686}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Olympic Village Double Chocolate Muffins Ingredients Makes about 9 jumbo muffins (be sure to get a jumbo pan for the best results) 1 Stick (8 Tablespoons) of Unsalted Butter, softened \\u00bd cup Canola or Vegetable Oil 1 Cup Sugar 1 Tablespoon Pure vanilla extract 3 Large Eggs 1 Packet (1.4 oz/39grams) instant chocolate pudding mix (Jello brand preferred) 1 \\u00bd Cups Cake Flour (Not Self-Rising) \\u00bd Cup Dark Cocoa Powder (Such as Dutch Processed) 1 Teaspoon Baking soda 1 \\u00bd Teaspoon Baking powder 3/4 tsp Fine table salt 1 cup Sour Cream 1/3 Cup Buttermilk 1 \\u00bd Cups Semi-Sweet Chocolate Chunks (I like enjoy life brand) Ganache: 1 (14 oz) can of Sweetened condensed milk 1 1/4 cups Bittersweet chocolate chips (Ghiardelli is my favorite) \\u00bc teaspoon pure vanilla extract#olympics#paris2024#olympicsmuffin#chocolatemuffin#olympicvillage#olympicmuffin The muffins at the Olympic Village are believed to be produced by French producer Coup de Pates.\", \"from\": 3688, \"to\": 4634, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3862, \"end\": 3868, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Butter\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.868506436715162e-85, \"text\": \"Butter\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Butter\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Butter\"}, {\"begin\": 4119, \"end\": 4124, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dutch_language\", \"score\": 0.9974102535217739, \"rank\": 0.0021970504660964213, \"text\": \"Dutch\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dutch_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dutch_language\"}, {\"begin\": 4337, \"end\": 4361, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Condensed_milk\", \"s